name: Mario Metaverse
description:
Mario Metaverse! - This future
is coming and every pop
culture will adapt. This is how I
imagine the iconic Mario will
be like when he's in the
metaverse. - Artist note: I
wanted to be a game
developer when I was young.
Super Mario was my favorite
game ever as a kid! Things
didn’t turn out that way but I
still get to make this kind of
animation for a living.
